Project Overview
This project focuses on building a Content-Based Movie Recommendation System using the TMDB 5000 Movie Dataset.
The recommender system suggests movies similar to a selected movie based on textual features such as:
•	Movie Overview 
•	Genres 
•	Cast 
•	Keywords 
The project uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques and Cosine Similarity to generate recommendations.
________________________________________
🎯 Project Objective
The objective of this project is to build an intelligent movie recommendation engine that recommends movies based on movie content rather than user ratings.
The recommendation system analyzes movie metadata and identifies movies with similar characteristics.
