⚙️ Project Workflow
1️⃣ Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
Tasks Performed
•	Merged datasets (movies.csv and credits.csv) 
•	Selected important columns: 
o	overview 
o	genres 
o	keywords 
o	cast 
o	crew 
Feature Engineering
Combined:
•	Overview 
•	Genres 
•	Keywords 
•	Top Cast Members 
•	Director
Text Processing
•	Converted text to lowercase 
•	Removed spaces and punctuation
2️⃣ Vectorization
The textual data was converted into numerical vectors using:
CountVectorizer
or
TfidfVectorizer
Steps
•	Removed stopwords 
•	Limited features to most frequent words 
•	Created vector representation for each movie 
________________________________________
3️⃣ Similarity Calculation
Cosine similarity was used to measure similarity between movies.
cosine_similarity()
Similarity Score
•	0 → Completely different 
•	1 → Highly similar 
The similarity matrix helps identify movies with related content.
________________________________________
4️⃣ Recommendation Logic
A recommendation function was created:
recommend(movie_name)
Functionality
•	Takes movie title as input 
•	Finds similarity scores 
•	Sorts movies by similarity 
•	Returns top 5 recommended movies 
Example
Input:
recommend("Avatar")
Output:
•	Guardians of the Galaxy 
•	John Carter 
•	Star Trek 
•	Interstellar 
•	The Matrix 
