📊 Key Insights
1.	Movies with similar genres and themes are grouped effectively. 
2.	Cast and director information significantly improve recommendation quality. 
3.	NLP-based vectorization helps identify semantic similarity. 
4.	Content-based filtering works well for new users without rating history. 
5.	Cosine similarity provides fast and accurate recommendations. 
